title: GAN 356 i Carry 3x3 (Magnetic)
body_html:
The 356 i Carry is the latest magnetic smart cube released by GAN. Unlike other GAN smart cube, this one features improved performance that is comparable to the 2020 flagship, the GAN 11 M Pro and the concept of an interchangeable battery is very convenient for some!

Some Interesting Features:

Charging: Instead of a charger, this cube is powered by replaceable coin batteries. A pre-installed battery is good for 280 hours of use before it needs to be changed.

Bluetooth Functionality: Connect your GAN cube to the upgraded Cube Station app in your phone via Bluetooth and enjoy many cool features! The Cube Station app will give you statistics based on your solve times, training exercises, races with cubers across the world, and more!

(get the app here: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gan.cubestation&hl=en_IN&gl=US)

title: MoYu RS Pyraminx M (Maglev) (Refurbished)
body_html:
The MoYu RS Pyraminx M (MagLev) is a cutting-edge and highly advanced puzzle cube that brings a new level of excitement to the world of Pyraminx solving. This innovative cube is designed to challenge and engage both beginners and seasoned cubers alike with its magnetic levitation technology, smooth rotations, and high-quality construction. Whether you're a competitive speedcuber or simply enjoy solving puzzles as a hobby, the MoYu RS Pyraminx MagLev Magnetic promises a thrilling and rewarding experience.

Key Features:

  • Magnetic Levitation Technology: The standout feature of the MoYu RS Pyraminx M (MagLev) is its magnetic levitation mechanism. Instead of traditional ball bearings, this cube utilizes powerful magnets for seamless and precise alignment of the layers, resulting in smooth and effortless turning.

  • High-Quality Materials: Crafted with precision and durability in mind, this Pyraminx is made from high-quality ABS plastic that is resistant to wear and tear, ensuring that it can withstand countless solves and maintain its performance over time.

  • Sculpted and Stickerless Design: The cube's ergonomic design and stickerless, vivid color scheme not only enhance its aesthetic appeal but also improve grip and visibility during solves, allowing for faster and more accurate movements.

  • Adjustable Tension and Tensioning System: Customization is key for speedcubers, and the MoYu RS Pyraminx M (MagLev) offers an adjustable tensioning system that allows you to fine-tune the cube's tension according to your preferences, enabling smoother and more controlled solves.

  • Excellent Corner Cutting: With its precise engineering and magnetic levitation, this Pyraminx boasts exceptional corner cutting abilities, making it easier to execute complex algorithms and turns without lockups or catching.

  • Competition-Ready: Designed with the needs of competitive cubers in mind, the MoYu RS Pyraminx M (MagLev) meets the standards for official World Cube Association (WCA) competitions, making it an ideal choice for those looking to take their Pyraminx solving skills to the next level.

  • Challenging and Fun: Whether you're a Pyraminx enthusiast looking for a new challenge or a beginner seeking to improve your puzzle-solving skills, this cube offers a satisfying blend of complexity and enjoyment, ensuring that every solve is a rewarding experience.

The MoYu RS Pyraminx M (MagLev) is a groundbreaking addition to the world of Pyraminx puzzles, combining cutting-edge technology with excellent build quality to provide an exciting and challenging solving experience for cubers of all levels. It's not just a puzzle; it's a revolution in Pyraminx solving.

Features Maglev technology, replacing springs with opposing magnets for reduced friction and faster turns. Comes with UV coating for improved durability and a superior grip.

The ballcore versions enhance stability and prevent pops, ensuring a reliable solving experience.

A sleek, glossy finish that improves grip, resists wear, and provides a premium feel.

✔ SPRING OR MAGLEV OPTIONS ⚙️🔄

title: Maglev Conversion Kit
body_html:
Upgrade your favorite speed cubes with the Cubelelo MagLev Conversion Kit! This kit is designed to replace traditional springs with Ring Magnets, utilizing Magnetic Levitation technology for faster, smoother, and frictionless turns. The kit includes 12 powerful magnets to boost stability, making your solves quicker and more precise. The magnets come in a convenient storage bottle, simplifying installation.

DISCLAIMER: This product is NON RETURNABLE.

How to Use:

  1. Open the 6 center caps of each side, one by one.
  2. Loosen the screws using a screwdriver.
  3. Remove the centerpiece.
  4. Take out the springs and screw.
  5. Replace the spring with 2 ring magnets on each side.
  6. Place one ring magnet on the screw and one in the centerpiece, ensuring the opposite poles face each other for magnetic repulsion.
  7. Reassemble by tightening the screws as per your preference.

This kit works with many popular cubes, including:

  • MoYu RS3M v5 3x3 Magnetic (Non - Adjustable)
  • MoYu RS3M v5 3x3 Magnetic (Dual - Adjustable)
  • MoYu MeiLong 3C 3x3
  • Drift 3M 3x3
  • Drift 3M PLUS 3x3
  • MoYu RS3M 3x3 Magnetic

The MoYu RS Pyraminx M (MagLev) is a groundbreaking addition to the world of Pyraminx puzzles, combining cutting-edge technology with excellent build quality to provide an exciting and challenging solving experience for cubers of all levels. title: 100 Numbers Board Teaching Aid
body_html:
NUMBERS LEARNING: The 100 numbers board is an educational tool designed to help children learn numbers from 1 to 100. The board typically has a grid of 10 rows and 10 columns, with each square containing a number from 1 to 100.

HANDS-ON-LEARNING: The board is designed to be hands-on, with children placing numbers onto the board to learn the sequence of numbers, counting, and basic math operations. The board can be used in various ways, such as matching numbers, filling in missing numbers, or creating patterns. 

MULTIFUNCTIONAL: The board is multifunctional and can be used for a range of activities. For example, it can be used for number recognition, counting, addition, subtraction, and even multiplication. It is an excellent tool to introduce children to basic math concepts in a fun and interactive way.

IMPROVES PROBLEM SOLVING SKILLS:  As children use the board to solve problems, it helps to develop their problem-solving skills. They learn to use logic and reasoning to fill in the missing numbers or solve simple math equations.

EASY TO USE: The 100 numbers board learning toy is easy to use and can be enjoyed by children of all ages. It is a great tool for parents and teachers to use in the classroom or at home to teach kids basic math concepts in an engaging and interactive way.

 

HOW TO PLAY:

The 100 numbers board includes wooden number blocks that can be made magnetic by sticking the magnetic tile under it. There are multiple ways by which you can play this board game such as:

  • Children can learn to count and identify numbers from 1-100 by placing the magnetic number blocks in the numbered tin case. 
  • Use the symbol and number blocks to create your own mathematical problems.
  • Hide the numbers on the tin case with the magnetic puzzle pieces and write the correct number that must come at that place by using the included temporary marker pen.
  • Use the red/blue chips to identify and create patterns on the number board. For example, ask your child to create a pattern and place chips on every other number or create a pattern with odd or even numbers like covering the odd number with blue and even number with red colored chips.
  • Two 10 sided dice are included in the box which can be used to play number games.
  • The magnetic square blocks can be utilized to grasp a multitude of mathematical concepts such as place values, multiplication, factions, rounding off, identifying patterns in odd and even numbers, and many more.
  • Can be used for both learning and developing number comparison skills with the help of the "<",">" and "=" operator sets included in the box.
  • Children can exercise their puzzle-solving abilities by creating and solving various puzzles. For instance, you could use the number pieces ranging from 1 to 6 to create a puzzle where you must select three numbers whose sum is equal to 10.
  • Can be used to play Sudoku on the grid platform of the box that can help cultivate observation and logical abilities.

Note: Pieces has to be made magnetic by sticking the tile on back of the square pieces

title: GAN Megaminx v2 MagLev (Magnetic)
body_html:
The GAN Megaminx V2 Magnetic (MagLev) is the pinnacle of speedcubing innovation, designed to elevate your solving experience to new heights. With its cutting-edge MagLev technology, this Megaminx replaces traditional springs with magnetic repulsion, offering faster and smoother turns while eliminating spring noise. Its ball-core design enhances stability, ensuring seamless performance even during high-speed solves. The GES v2 tensioning system allows for 36 unique configurations, letting you fine-tune the cube to your exact preferences. Featuring a dimpled exterior for superior grip and a honeycomb surface for optimized lubricant distribution, the GAN Megaminx V2 Magnetic (MagLev) is built for speedcubers who demand precision, comfort, and durability.

Key Features

  • MagLev Technology: Magnetic repulsion system replaces springs for smoother, faster turns and noise-free performance.
  • Auto-Alignment Mechanism: Delivers ~15-degree auto-alignment, ensuring precise and effortless corner turns.
  • GES v2 Tensioning System: Offers 36 customizable tension settings to suit your unique solving style and speed preferences.
  • Ball-Core Design: Provides superior stability and balance, minimizing lockups and enhancing control during solves.
  • Dimpled Exterior: Improves grip for secure handling, even during extended solving sessions.
  • Honeycomb Surface: Ensures even lubricant distribution, delivering consistent smoothness over time.

title: Speedstacks G5 Pro Timer
body_html:

Embark on a cubing journey like never before with the DaYan GuHong Pro MagLev – where classic craftsmanship meets cutting-edge technology. Crafted by the renowned DaYan, this speedcube sets a new standard for 3x3 cubes, delivering magnetic precision and seamless turns for an unparalleled solving experience. 🚀

MagLev features

  • Magnetic repulsion technology
  • No springs required
  • Faster turning feel

Key features

  • Auto-alignment turning (~15 degrees)
  • Magnetic core corner/core magnets for a better, more controllable turning feel
  • 5 tension settings (no tool required)
  • "Anti-stick" piece design

Overview

  • Smooth, fast turning
  • Frosted exterior finish

Unleash precision and speed with the DaYan GuHong Pro MagLev – your ultimate choice for a blend of classic design and cutting-edge performance. 🌟

title: Jungle Safari 2-in-1 Magnetic Board Game
body_html:
FEATURES: The Jungle Safari 2-in-1 Magnetic Board game consists of over 100+ colorful different animals-themed pieces with full magnetic backing. This game also comes with a model book where you can look for inspiration and ideas. Use your imagination to create different scenes and figures on the slate using the chalks and water-based marker pen which you can later erase to reuse the slate.

TWO SIDES/ MULTIFUNCTIONAL BLACKBOARD: The lid of the box serves as a magnetic board, the black side can be used for drawing with chalk, on the white magnetic side, children can play puzzle game with colorful jigsaw puzzle pieces and draw with the water-based marker pen.

MULTIFUNCTIONAL EDUCATIONAL TOY/ EDUCATIONAL TOY: The game encourages children's imagination and lets them create endless scenarios and pictures using a drawing board and a magnetic board with various puzzle pieces. It is a great tool for practicing fine motor skills, concentration and creativity. It encourages children's creativity and imagination and hand-eye coordination.

PREMIUM MATERIAL: Made with High-quality wood with uniform and fine texture jigsaw puzzle pieces made with non-toxic material, finely cut and polished. The wooden box is cleverly designed, all small parts can be easily stored in the box. This puzzle is completely safe for your child to play and learn with.

ULTIMATE GIFT IDEA: It’s a perfect gift for children to learn and have fun with this magnetic puzzle. Gift it on any occasion and create new memories with your loved ones.

title: Drift 2x2, 3x3, Pyraminx & Silver Mirror Gift Box
body_html: Experience elegance and challenge with the Drift collection, featuring the 2x2, 3x3, Pyraminx, and the stunning Silver Mirror cube. Perfect for the discerning puzzle enthusiast, this set combines style and sophistication with top-tier performance.

title: Drift 3x3, 4x4 & Pyraminx Gift Box
body_html:
Introducing our Drift Cube Gift Box! This set includes three mind-bending puzzles: the Drift 3x3 Cube, Drift 4x4 Cube, and Drift Pyraminx. The Drift 3x3 Cube offers a classic yet captivating challenge, while the Drift 4x4 Cube takes it up a notch. The Pyraminx adds a unique twist to the mix. Each puzzle is designed for smooth turns and hours of mental stimulation. It's the perfect gift for puzzle enthusiasts and those who love a good mental workout.

  • Drift Cube Gift Box: A set of three intriguing puzzles for hours of mental stimulation and entertainment.
  • Drift 3x3 Cube: Classic 3x3 Rubik's Cube with anti-pop design, smooth turns, and quality construction.
  • Drift 4x4 Cube: Advanced 4x4 Rubik's Cube with a frosted surface and durable construction, designed for precision and challenge.
  • Drift Pyraminx: A pyramid-shaped puzzle with smooth rotations, providing a unique twisty challenge.
  • Perfect Gift: Ideal for puzzle aficionados and those seeking a mental workout.
  • Durable Construction: Made with high-quality materials for long-lasting use.
  • Mind-Boggling Fun: Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned solver, this gift box will provide endless enjoyment and brain-teasing challenges.

title: Drift 3x3, 4x4 & Pyraminx Black Gift Box
body_html: The perfect gift set for puzzle enthusiasts, featuring high-quality, black 3x3 and 4x4 cubes alongside a Pyraminx. Ideal for all skill levels, offering a smooth and enjoyable solving experience.

title: Drift 3x3, Pyraminx & Silver Mirror Gift Box
Drift 3x3, Pyraminx Black & Silver Mirror Gift Box
YJ MGC 7x7 (Magnetic)
body_html:
YJ MGC 7x7 Magnetic is certainly one of the most popular 7x7's available! The MGC 7x7 does a great job of capturing YJ's signature turning feel and consistent magnet strength throughout all 7 layers which is a huge plus for us.

YJ's focus is quality at a lower price and they certainly have achieved this goal. If your turning style is very fast, we do suggest tightening the MGC 7 as they do come set more on the loose side out of the box. 

Included Accessories:

  • Tensioning Tool
  • Set of soft springs
  • Set of hard springs
  • Extra magnets
  • Cube Stand
  • Manual

title: QiYi Warrior Plus Max Box 3x3 (38 cms)
body_html:
QiYi Warrior Plus Big 3x3 (18.8cm) is one of the largest mass-production, fully functional 3x3s! The turning is still very smooth and easy to handle despite its size. This item is a perfect decoration and novelty item to enjoy!

QiYi Warrior Plus Max Massive 3x3 38cm (Standard) is ridiculously cool and actually turns very well since it is designed like a standard-size speed cube!

Whether you are looking for a fun cube to solve or the perfect cuber decoration/decor -- the Warrior Plus Max checks all the boxes!

title: QiYi Warrior Plus 3x3 (18.8 cms)
body_html:
Introducing the QiYi Warrior Plus Big 3x3 Cube, a remarkable addition to the world of cubing that pushes boundaries with its impressive size and exceptional functionality. At a staggering 18.8cm, this cube stands as one of the largest mass-produced 3x3 puzzles, providing enthusiasts with a unique and challenging solving experience. Despite its substantial dimensions, the cube's turning mechanism maintains an extraordinary level of smoothness, ensuring ease of handling even during intricate maneuvers. This cube transcends the ordinary, not only serving as a fully functional puzzle but also as a captivating decoration and novelty item that adds flair to any collection.

Key Features:

  • GARGANTUAN DIMENSIONS: With an expansive size of 18.8cm, the QiYi Warrior Plus offers cubers a distinctive and challenging puzzle-solving experience, making it one of the largest 3x3 cubes in mass production.
  • SMOOTH AND MANAGEABLE TURNING: Despite its substantial size, the cube boasts a remarkably smooth turning mechanism, providing users with an enjoyable and controlled solving experience.
  • FULLY FUNCTIONAL DESIGN: This cube is not just about size; it's a fully functional puzzle, allowing cubers to engage in intricate solving techniques and maneuvers.
  • UNIQUE DECORATIVE ELEMENT: Beyond its cubing functionality, the QiYi Warrior Plus serves as an eye-catching decoration, adding a touch of novelty and aesthetic appeal to any display or collection.
  • NOVELTY ENJOYMENT: As a novelty item, this cube goes beyond the conventional expectations of a puzzle, offering an element of enjoyment that extends beyond the solving process, making it an exciting and entertaining addition to any cuber's repertoire.
  • HIGH-QUALITY CONSTRUCTION: Crafted from durable materials, the QiYi Warrior Plus ensures longevity and reliability, making it suitable for extended use without compromising performance.
  • VERSATILE CHALLENGE: Suited for both enthusiasts seeking a new level of challenge and collectors looking to diversify their array, this cube caters to a broad spectrum of interests within the cubing community.

Embark on a cubing adventure like never before with the QiYi Warrior Plus 3x3 Cube – an extraordinary blend of size, functionality, and novelty that redefines the possibilities of puzzle-solving.

title: Drift 3x3 Stickered
body_html: Cubelelo Drift is the latest cube by Cubelelo. It has amazing corner cutting, higher stability, and an optimized structure of anti-pop to make sure all parts of the speed cube will not pop out during fast rotation solves. The hand feel of drift gives a wonderful feel while solving. The cube comes tensioned and lubed already, however, we recommend buying Cubelelo silicon lubricants for more lubrication and smoothness. Made of ABS material this cube has a frosted surface and is wear-resistant and durable.

title: Drift Rainbow Ball Mini (8 Holes)
body_html:
The Drift Rainbow Ball is an easy puzzle where you move the balls around, trying to match them with their matching rings. It's a simple game, making it perfect for beginners or kids who want a fun and not-too-hard.

Rainbow Ball is, as suggested by the name, a ball shaped challenge. The ball is filled with a bunch of round holes. The holes are all filled with a smaller ball except for one of them. The smaller balls can be pushed into the empty hole, as long as they are adjacent to it and because of this the Rainbow Ball is essentially a 3D klotski puzzle. The ball is extra fun as it can be used both for playing with as a ball and for brain teasing as a puzzle.

title: Drift Gear 3x3 v2
body_html:
The 3x3 Gear Cube is an eye-catching puzzle to say the least! Equipped with plastic tiles and a sturdy mechanism, this puzzle is fun and challenging to solve!

The Gear Cube V2 features gears that rotate the edge pieces as the cube is turned. In this version, one axis of rotation features normal 3x3 movement, whereas the other 2 have normal gear cube rotations. It feels sturdy and turns smoothly right out of the box.

body_html:
• EXCITING SCI-FI ADVENTURE: Not just an ordinary cube; features holographic images that emerge during solving, creating a thrilling cosmic journey.
  • COSMIC APPEARANCE: Advanced UV printing showcases holographic depictions of stars, planets, and celestial wonders.
  • SPACE-TACULAR DESIGN: Combines puzzle-solving with the magnificence of outer space, perfect for young minds.

title: Cubelelo Ball In The Cage Puzzle
body_html:
Cubelelo Ball In The Cage Puzzle

The Cubelelo Ball In The Cage Puzzle is the new budget-friendly Brain Teaser. The aim of this charming wooden puzzle is to solve the fetch in the cage. Upon first glance, it may seem impossible to solve and fit through the spaces between. With a little patience and clever thinking. Solve the jigsaw and creates advanced patterns.

title: Drift 2x2 Silver Mirror & 3x3 Silver Mirror Gift Box
body_html:
UNIQUE GEOMETRIC DISTORTION: The Drift 2x2 Silver Mirror & 3x3 Silver Mirror Combo introduces a fun and artistic twist to cubing. Both the 2x2 and 3x3 cubes feature irregular shapes and reflective, mirror-like stickers that create stunning geometric illusions.

VARIED DIFFICULTY LEVELS: This combo set caters to a broad range of solvers. The 2x2 mirror cube offers a manageable introduction to mirror cube solving, while the 3x3 mirror cube presents a more challenging experience for intermediate and advanced cubers.

REFLECTIVE STICKERS: The mirror cubes are adorned with high-quality reflective stickers that give off a captivating, shimmering effect as you solve them. These stickers are not only visually appealing but also durable.

ANTI-POP AND ANTI-LOCK DESIGN: These mirror cubes are designed to reduce the likelihood of pops and lockups, allowing for a smooth solving process without interruptions.

AESTHETIC AND DECORATIVE: When not in use, the Mirror Cube Combo Set doubles as a stunning and conversation-starting piece of decorative art. Display it on your desk or bookshelf, and it's sure to capture the attention of anyone who sees it.

body_html:
UNIQUE SHAPE: Drift Square-1 & Skewb are renowned for their unique shape. The Square-1 can be manipulated into various irregular shapes, while the Skewb features rotating axes that add a new dimension to your cubing experience.

TWO DISTINCT PUZZLES: This combo set includes two different puzzles, each with its own set of solving strategies. The Square-1 and Skewb cater to a wide range of cubing preferences and skill levels.

SMOOTH AND PRECISE TURNING: Both puzzles feature internal mechanisms that allow for smooth and precise turning. The well-engineered designs ensure that you can make accurate moves as you attempt to solve these shape-shifting challenges.

UNIQUE AESTHETICS: The Square-1 and Skewb cubes boast distinctive and eye-catching designs.

BRAIN-TEASING CHALLENGES: Solving the Square-1 and Skewb engages your spatial and geometrical thinking skills, making them ideal for those who enjoy a more abstract and intellectually stimulating solving experience.

GREAT FOR ALL SKILL LEVELS: This combo set is suitable for cubers of all skill levels, from beginners looking to expand their puzzle-solving abilities to advanced solvers seeking unique challenges.

title: Cube Timer Data Cord (3.5mm - 3.5mm)
body_html:
Cube Timer Data Cord

Timer Data Cord is a standard 3.5mm to 3.5mm cable that can be used to connect your timer to your computer, mobile phone, or Speedstack display. It is 150 cm long and features stereo output. To connect the Drift timer to your display, computer, or mobile phone, it must be plugged into the microphone port(make sure it has one) and used with a compatible program.
Note* The Data Cord is Either Connected to the Desktop or Dual Connecting Ports Available Laptops.
Compatibility: The cord can be compatible with all timers with a 3.5 MM audio jack like QiYi timer, Drift Timer,  QiYi Smart Timer, etc. 
(Incompatible with Speedstacks timers)

title: Drift Gear 3x3 BYOB
body_html:
Cubelelo Drift Gear 3x3 gear cube with black base plastic tile has new and advanced designs. The cube has 12 edge pieces, four on every layer, which is all gear cogs. Each edge piece has two different colors on it, the colors of the two sides it lies between.

It also has eight corners, four on the top layer and four on the bottom layer. Each corner connects three different sides and possesses those three colors.

title: Drift Square-1 BYOB
body_html:
Check out Drift Square-1! This is the first entry level square-1 to be released from Cubelelo and it features the popular "frosted" plastic for the Stickerless variant which improves grip and looks spectacular. The Drift Square-1 is now available! As part of the Drift series, the Drift Square-1 delivers excellent speedsolving performance at a great price.


The Drift Square-1 offers brilliant performance and is capable of achieving record-setting times straight out of the box. The cube cuts corners incredibly well for a Square-1. The puzzle is pre-lubricated from the factory, and it turns very smoothly OOB. The puzzle is adjustable with the help of screws just like other speedcubes, stable and doesn’t pop. When using it, you can expect smooth layer rotations and very controllable speed.


For a long time there hasn’t really been a Square-1 that sticks out, but this one does. This cube is sure to be popular with beginner and intermediate solvers alike. If you’re looking for the absolute best Square-1 on the market then you’re in the right place.

title: Drift Pyraminx M (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html:
The Drift Pyraminx M (Magnetic) is a newly launched Pyraminx by Cubelelo that has just hit the market. Medium strength magnets combine with a new design delivering a smooth, fast, and stable Pyraminx, and an overall great performing puzzle. The new design is surprisingly comfortable and easy to hold and grip.

FEATURES:

  1. Magnetic: The Drift Pyraminx M (Magnetic) is equipped with 48 Neodymium Magnets inside each piece, which provides added stability and alignment to the puzzle.

  2. Smooth turning: The magnets in the Pyraminx allow for smoother and more precise turning, making the puzzle easier to solve.

  3. Durable construction: It is is made of durable ABS plastic, which can withstand frequent use and wear.

  4. Comes pre-lubricated: Drift Pyraminx M comes pre-lubricated, making it even smoother to turn and solve right out of the box.

  5. Portable and compact: This Pyraminx is a compact and portable puzzle, making it easy to carry and solve on-the-go.

title: Drift Mirror Cube BYOB
body_html:
The Cubelelo Drift Mirror Cube is the new budget-friendly shape mod. Solving the Mirror Cube is exactly the same as solving a Cube; however, it is harder to identify each part because the size difference between the puzzle's parts is less obvious than the color difference of the original puzzle's stickers. If you are a puzzle collector, self-challenger, or just want to solve a mirror block, you should get this.

Disclaimer : The mirror cubes have a glossy finish so it may have minor scratches right from the manufacturing step which will not affect the overall functionality of the cube.

title: Drift Skewb BYOB
body_html: Cubelelo Drift Skewb Stickerless is a new entry-level skewb that has just hit the market. With many modern features and a very affordable price, the Drift Skewb is expected to make the skewb puzzle event more accessible to all speedcubers of all ages.

title: Drift Megaminx M (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html: The new Cubelelo Drift Megaminx M (Magnetic) is a newly launched megaminx by Cubelelo that has just hit the market. Medium strength magnets combine with a new design delivering a smooth, fast, and stable megaminx, and an overall great performing puzzle. The new circular ridge design is surprisingly comfortable and easy to hold and grip. This expected to make the megaminx puzzle event more accessible to all speedcubers of all ages.

title: Drift Mastermorphix BYOB
body_html:
Cubelelo Drift Mastermorphix High Speed Cube is one of the best and most underrated cubes currently on the market, especially considering it is so inexpensive. The cube has a buttery smooth feel, with a more stable feel. This, combined with the slightly clacky sound of the cube makes it extremely pleasant to play with. This cube is extremely fast, so some users, especially those with more aggressive turning styles, may find this cube difficult to control.


Corner cutting on this cube far exceeds what any user would require. The cube can easily corner cut well over 45 degrees, and reverse cuts about 3/4ths of a cube. Corner twists are not an issue on this cube, either, though I have experienced one or two during solves. Overall, this is an excellent speedcube, and recommended to any cuber who is comfortable controlling fast cubes. The Cubelelo Drift Mastermorphix Stickerless is pillowed with bright coloured frosted plastic. It turns very smooth. A mastermorphix is a pyramid-shaped 3x3 shape modification puzzle and is solved like one.

featured_image.alt: Cubelelo Drift Mastermorphix Stickerless

title: Drift 7M 7x7 (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html: Cubelelo Drift 7M 7x7 (Magnetic) is a newly launched budget-friendly magnetic 7x7 from Cubelelo. This Cube offers a surprisingly high level of quality and performance. The extremely smooth outer layers, mixed with a medium to light magnetic feel, make this puzzle a pleasure to turn. This is an excellent choice for all skill levels.

featured_image.alt: Cubelelo Drift 7M 7x7 (Magnetic)

title: Drift 6M 6x6 (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html:
Cubelelo Drift 6M 6x6 (Magnetic) is a brand new cube from Cubelelo. This Cube offers a surprisingly high level of quality and performance. The internal mechanism includes unerring magnetic for positioning, double corner feet, and deep anti-sticky mechanism.

The cube is designed with a multiple inner hole mechanism that enlarges the contact of the face, enhances the stability during turning, and avoids the layers' confusion. The deep anti-sticky structure makes the performance of the cube outstanding. And the structure of the inner core is designed in such a way that it will avoid the pigment effect from the friction surface. The outstanding performance of the cube will make the cubers go back to solve it again and again.

featured_image.alt: Cubelelo Drift 6M 6x6 (Magnetic)

title: Drift 5M 5x5 (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html:
Cubelelo Drift 5M 5x5 Magnetic is one of Cubelelo's most affordable magnetic cube offerings. This budget magnetic 5x5 is crispier and more stable thanks to the introduction of unique magnetic elements with a lightweight and stickerless-matte surface finish design this cube is the perfect choice for fast and controllable cube lovers.

A tactile and very stable feel with clean, clicky feedback regardless of piece orientation is achieved due to this magnetization effect. The magnetic attraction between the pieces results in increased efficiency while minimizing overshooting and undesirable lockups.

title: Drift 4M 4x4 (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html:
Cubelelo Drift 4M 4x4 (Magnetic) is our budget magnetic 4x4 offering. The cube is very stable, thanks to the introduction of unique magnetic elements.

We have introduced ninety-six neodymium magnets of suitable strength at various strategic locations in the cube, arranged in a way to ensure precise symmetric pattern while rotation.

A tactile and stable feel with clean, clicky feedback regardless of piece orientation is achieved due to this magnetization effect. The magnetic attraction between the pieces results in increased efficiency while minimizing overshooting and undesirable lockups crispier and more stable. The magnetic attraction between the pieces results in increased efficiency while minimizing overshooting and undesirable lockups.

title: Drift 3M 3x3 (Magnetic) BYOB
body_html:
Cubelelo Drift 3M 3x3 Magnetic Stickerless is one of Cubelelo's most affordable magnetic cube offerings. This budget magnetic 3x3 is crispier and more stable thanks to the introduction of unique magnetic elements. title: Wooden Rings Stacking Tower
body_html:
FEATURES: A wooden rings stacking tower is a colorful and educational stacking game designed for children. The game consists of wooden arches in different sizes and colors that can be stacked to create a tower that resembles a rainbow.

OBJECTIVE: The goal of the game is to stack the arches in descending order from largest to smallest, creating a rainbow tower.

HIGH-QUALITY MATERIAL: The wooden rings stacking tower is made from high-quality, non-toxic materials that are safe for children to play with. The game is easy to clean and maintain, making it a durable and long-lasting addition to any child's toy collection.

BENEFITS: Wooden rings stacking tower are designed to promote creativity, problem-solving, and fine motor skills in children. The game can also help teach children about colors, sizes, and spatial relationships.

ENGAGING TOY: The Wooden rings stacking tower is a fun and engaging game that can provide hours of entertainment for children while also promoting their development and learning.

HOW TO PLAY: The wooden rings should be arranged in descending order from largest to smallest. Place the largest arch on a flat surface, such as a table or floor. Then, take the second largest arch and place it on top of the first one, making sure that the curved ends match up. Repeat this process with the remaining arches, building a tower that resembles a rainbow.

body_html:

The cards contain some interesting and colorful illustrations that relate to the content of the card.

The wooden stick included in the kit can be used for pointing out the letters on the card.

title: Wooden Rainbow Tower
body_html:
• TOWER OF HANOI: The Wooden Rainbow Tower, originally known as Tower of Hanoi is a mathematical game consisting of three rods and 8 disks of various diameters,  which can slide onto any rod. It is an ancient puzzle invented by a French mathematician in 1883. 
  • INTERACTIVE PUZZLE: It can be used to teach kids to learn colors, sizes and numbers but can be played by all ages because of its increasing complexity when the number of disks are increased.
  • PREMIUM QUALITY: This wooden rainbow tower is made of premium quality wood which is  non-toxic, well polished and without any sharp chamfers. The colored wooden rings are vibrant with smooth round edges.
  • BENEFITS: It can develop logical and mathematical abilities, cultivate eye-hand coordination ability, train muscle reflexes. It is used for both education and entertainment and also helps in brain development. 
  • FOR ALL AGES: Suitable for all ages, this Wooden Rainbow Tower  is a great gift for  friends, family, coworkers or yourself. Gift it on any occasion, be it Birthdays, Father's Day, Mother's day or festivals.

 

HOW TO PLAY:

The objective of the game is to move all the pieces from the first tower to the third tower.

RULES : 

  1. You are allowed to move only one disk at a time.
  2. You can only transfer the top disk of one stack to another rod.
  3. You cannot place the larger disk on the smaller disk

title: MoYu WeiLong WR M Lite 3x3 (Magnetic)
body_html:
The MoYu WeiLong WR M is MoYu's a flagship cube.This updated design now features adjustable magnets along with the standard MoYu spring compression/tension system. It offers a softer feel and more customization at a lower price!

The cube features a 55mm compact size, smaller than conventional cubes, more controllable, with better hold and grip. It gives us 9 Levels of elasticity and 5 Levels of Magnet Strength that's a total of 45 customization settings. title: Cubicle Labs Lubes
body_html:
Cubicle Labs DNM-37 🌊
Get ready to elevate your puzzle game with DNM-37, a water-based lube designed by Cubicle Labs! This magic potion creates a refreshing burst of speed for your puzzles 🧩💨. It absorbs moisture from the air, keeping you fast and efficient for a long time 🔄. Perfect for all your favorites, from minxes to Square-1s and big cubes! 

Cubicle Labs Mystic 🌿
Experience smoothness like never before with Mystic! This plant-based lube is the world’s first to harness the power of aloe, delivering a lively, quick feel that you can both see and hear 📣. Just remember, it's best used within a year and avoid it if you have an aloe allergy! ⚠️❌

Important: Don’t ingest, apply near eyes or ears, or set it on fire! 🔥🚫 Keep the cap closed when not in use.

Cubicle Labs Silk 🌈
Introducing the new and improved Silk!  This reformulated version keeps the plush, controllable feel you love while enhancing your puzzle experience even more! 🧩 Ideal for puzzles of all sizes, from minxes to big cubes! 🏆

Disclaimer: Safe to touch, but please don’t ingest, ignite, or expose to extreme heat! 🔥🚫

Instructions:

  1. Add 2 drops of lube to your puzzle. 
  2. Break it in and feel the magic happen! 🛠️
  3. Buckle up—things are about to get FAST! 🚀

Important: Avoid applying lube to hardware! Water-based lubes can cause rust on screws or springs. 🛑🧪

Note: The color of the lube may slightly vary! 🌈

featured_image.alt: Cubicle Labs DNM-37

Indulge in the ultimate puzzle-solving experience with the Drift Axis, Fisher & Windmill (Tiled) Gift Box. This exquisite set features three distinct puzzles meticulously crafted with a stunning design, tiled surface, and premium finish.

  • Appearance: Tiled surface cubes have colored tiles or pieces embedded directly into the surface of the cube. Each tile represents a different color, eliminating the need for traditional stickers.
  • Durability: The v2 is of better quality & more sturdy. The tiles on these cubes are typically more durable than stickers, as they are less prone to peeling or fading over time.
  • Texture: Tiled cubes have a more enhanced texture compared to stickerless or stickered cubes with an overall premium hand feel.
  • Solving Experience: the v2 version is smoother as compared to the stickerless one giving you the ultimate solving experience.

title: Drift Mirror Cube
body_html:
The Cubelelo Drift Mirror Cube is the new budget-friendly shape mod. Solving the Mirror Cube is exactly the same as solving a Cube; however, it is harder to identify each part because the size difference between the puzzle's parts is less obvious than the color difference of the original puzzle's stickers. If you are a puzzle collector, self-challenger, or just want to solve a mirror block, you should get this.

Disclaimer : The mirror cubes have a glossy finish so it may have minor scratches right from the manufacturing step which will not affect the overall functionality of the cube.
